{"title":"使者  一个邮人的陨逝","authors":["王明方"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":10,"day":15}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"使者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个邮人的陨逝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王明方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的眼睛里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蜿蜒着重重邮路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你，一个背负邮包竞走的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使者，缓缓的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坠倒了，缓缓的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天空没有一只鸟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有一丝虚拟的痕迹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邮路笔直地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经过你最初的衣袖摆动的方向"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你卧成山脉的姿势"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无声无息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使者，你的微笑依旧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"筑起无数条永久安详的线条"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邮路穿透胸肋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"目光被惊起的雁子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驮起，落下又驮起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而你，依旧静静的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在踏实的泥土下面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"静静的，邮路蜿蜒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一条绸质的挽带飘动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一圈黑纱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缠在我心里"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}